data.description: PRICE REDUCED!!Seller offers$10,000 in concessions. Come & see this conveniently located, charming, well priced home. 3 Bed, 2 Bath w/ large living area. Kitchen offers plenty of cabinets, stylish back splash, nice & useful island w/ granite countertops. Ceramic tile throughout. Primary bedroom features a private bathroom w/ double vanity & well-sized mirror closet door. Large family room w/ skylights that provide natural light. Enjoy your early morning coffee or relaxing afternoon on the comfortable and covered patio. Bonus room with exit door(4th room)This home offers tons of opportunity to be creative in this well sized backyard. Driveway features double gates with lots of parking spaces. Exterior of the home has been given a stucco finish. Extra Room used as a 4th bedroom can easily be converted to an office.
